  "bodyHtml": "<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>What’s Trade-in?</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trade-in is a simple tool that allows refurbishers to source devices directly from Back Market customers. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>How does it work?</strong></span></h2>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Create listings in the Trade-in section of your Back Office. Choose the items you want and the price you’ll pay for each grade (there are 4 functional and 2 non-functional grades).</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Customers assess their items on Back Market. We offer them the Trade-in BackBox price to the customer according to the corresponding grading of the item. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Trade-in-BackBox-How-does-it-work\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;text-decoration: underline;\">Learn more about Trade-in Backbox here.</a></strong></span></span></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you offer the BackBox price and the customer accepts the offer, an order is created in your Back Office. </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Back Market takes care of the logistics. You&#39;ll receive the items at the address you provided.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Once received, you audit the items and trigger the payment on the transaction from your account. </span></li></ol>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Why should you take advantage of Trade-in?</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>1. Wide range of items:</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5 categories of products: </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Smartphones </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tablets </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Consoles </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Audio</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">MacBooks</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2. Significant business opportunity:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>High volumes:</strong> There are 100,000 items traded-in in the EU &amp; UK and 40,000 items traded-in in the US per month</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Strong growth:</strong> + 40% per year</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>Margin VAT eligible</b></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>You can choose your payment method by default:</strong> Direct debit (through SEPA in the EU, BACS in the UK) or credit card</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>3. Easy to manage:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Same Back Office, same Back Market contact</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Back Market handles the logistics part and the logistics fees are fixed</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trade-in is subscription-free and commitment-free</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Logistics costs and commission are paid by the seller only if the order is completed</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>4. Fees</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"width: 99.9729%;border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;height: 447.917px;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr style=\"height: 34.401px;\"><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 15.2284%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Activity</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 46.6839%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Compensation</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Details</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Amount</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"height: 55.1823px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"9\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 15.2284%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">TRADE-IN</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 46.6839%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Commission on Trade-in (total amount paid by Refurbisher incl. taxes and shipping fees)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10% (excl. tax) on all Products</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">-</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 55.1823px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 46.6839%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trade-in Logistic fees</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">in France, Spain, and Germany</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Smartphones and audio</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">11.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 34.401px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">MacBooks, video game consoles</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">14.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 34.401px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tablets</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">13.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 55.1823px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 46.6839%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trade-in Logistic fees</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">in the UK</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Smartphones and audio</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 55.1823px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">MacBooks, video game consoles, and tablets</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">13.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 55.1823px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 46.6839%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trade-in Logistic fees</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">in other countries</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Smartphones and audio</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">12.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 34.401px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">MacBooks, video game consoles</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">15.90 €</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 34.401px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.2101%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tablets</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 9.86104%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">13.90 €</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong></strong></span></h3>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Main rule</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>1. Processing time:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In order to meet our customers&#39; expectations, we ask you to respect the processing deadlines of orders received:</span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">24 hours to respond to the customer</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">48 hours upon receiving an item to process the order</span></li></ul>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2. Eligibility:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You can use this service if:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You already sell on our platform</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You have a physical location (e.g. warehouse) to handle your Trade-in operations in one of the following countries: France, Germany, Spain, Italy, Belgium, Netherlands, Poland &amp; UK.</span></li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.backmarket.fr/bo-seller/feedback?formId=LxMCxr7i\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Request to join Trade-in here</strong></a></span> </span></span></h2>"
